title: Garrys.Mod.v13.12.06-v14.04.19.Update
description:
===========================================
Instructions
===========================================

1. Extract all the contents from the rar file to your Garry's Mod folder and overwrite when asked

2. Set your name in LumaEmu.ini (instructions in README.txt)

3. Launch the game as usual

===========================================
Changelog v14.04.19.Update
===========================================

A shitload has been updated/fixed/added since v13.12.06
so I'm not going to write out the whole changelog.

Some of the most notable changes are:

- Fixed lamps projecting backwards
- Improved mounting system (better performance)
- Minor Half Life 2 campaign fixes
- Lots of requested Lua fixes and features

===========================================
